Installation
============

You will need:
    - a POSIXy system (Windows is not supported at present.)
    - rustup/Cargo
    - scdoc [0] and just [1]

Then:

+--------------------------------------------------------------------+
| $ ls                              # must be in root directory      |
| docs  examples INSTALL justfile pesc-cli pesc-lib README TODO      |
| # just install                    # install in /usr/local/, or...  |
| $ just prefix=~/local/ install    # install in ~/local/            |
+--------------------------------------------------------------------+

Consult pesc(7) and pescli(1) for usage information.

[0]: scdoc: https://git.sr.ht/~sircmpwn/scdoc
[1]: just:  https://github.com/casey/just
